data.description: Check out this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bath home! This beautiful property offers a fantastic opportunity for you to make it your dream home!! Step inside and prepare to be amazed by the impressive features and inviting atmosphere. Cool color tones give the home an airy/breezy feel! The spacious kitchen boasts ample GRANITE countertops, an abundance of cabinets, TWO pantries and a center island complete with a prep sink! The archways throughout the house add a touch of elegance and charm. Relaxation awaits in the expansive master bedroom offering his and hers walk in closets. The master bath features a walk in shower, a double vanity and a garden tub where you can soak away the stress of the day. The split plan layout ensures privacy and convenience for everyone in the household. Do you enjoy outdoor living? Look no further! Entertain guests or simply bask in the sun in your very own screened lanai and gleaming salt water pool. The pool and screened enclosure built in 2019 makes this a great escape for many years to come! The outdoor pool shower allows for refreshing rinses after taking a dip or working in your garden. But that's not all! The tiki hut on the pool deck adds a fun tropical vibe, perfect for summer cook outs, hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings under the stars. You can swim all year as this is a heated pool! Enjoy the private back yard surrounded by vinyl privacy fence. Situated in a centrally located neighborhood with gated entry, this property offers easy access to amenities, schools, parks, and more. With a two car garage, convenience is at your fingertips. Stacked stone accents on the front of the home complete the impressive curb appeal of this home! Add in the BRAND NEW ROOF (Sept 2023) and a NEW LENNOX AC in 2021, makes this home a great choice! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own this remarkable home with its attractive features and desirable location. Call now to schedule a viewing and make this house your new sanctuary! Check out the interactive virtual tour as well!
